Sure. I tried to turn off both substring and subwords, the performance go back to normal. And the major perf factor is the substring match.

Turn off substring match with vmArgs -Djdt.codeCompleteSubstringMatch=false or System.setProperty(AssistOptions.PROPERTY_SubstringMatch, "false")
Turn off subwords match with JavaCore.setOptions().

// JavaLanguageServerPlugin.java

public void start(BundleContext bundleContext) throws Exception {
    ...
    Hashtable<String, String> options = new Hashtable<>();
    options.put(AssistOptions.OPTION_SubwordMatch, AssistOptions.DISABLED);
    JavaCore.setOptions(options);
}
